text.tspan: Students at Miami University were surveyed to evaluate how price affected whether
a pizza was ordered from Pizza Hut or another pizzeria. Of the students, 28 were
told the regular Pizza Hut price and 35 were given a reduced price.
Is the probability of a pizza being ordered from Pizza Hut affected by the
The probability of ordering from Pizza Hut
increases by 10.7% when the price drops.
price? If so, by how much?
